title: Think in Black and White
itunes:title: Think in Black and White
description:
Episode 317 - Most of the time life is either yes or no, go or stop. If you think in black and white and not give yourself a ton of options, it allows you to make decisions quicker and execute. Check out this episode to learn how to be more decisive.
